Internet Package(s)
Router -> ISP : FIBER OPTICS

-------------------------------

Router -> Switch :  Straight-through Cable/Cat6 Cable/UTP
Switch -> Computer(s) : Straight-through Cable
Printer(s) -> Switch : Straight-through Cable
Raspberry Pi -> Switch : Straight-through Cable
Raspberry Pi -> Smart TV : HDMI Cable
NVR -> Switch : Ethernet Cable
Poe -> Switch : Ethernet Cable

